{
  "3148160": {
    "name": "龙之歌：美食与冒险",
    "steam_appid": 3148160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/f0ad2e59be71d22a0923d2eb281291ca.avif?t=1770897818\" width=493 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《龙之歌：美食与冒险》 讲述了一对冒险兄妹的故事。在一时冲动之下，妹妹格蕾西买下了一个小镇的海滨酒馆。没想到，在酒馆里发现了一只可爱的小龙。于是他们与这条小龙一起经营酒馆、结交新朋友，逐渐融入悠闲的新生活。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/e488c08c5975a1486c13179d7b142bc4.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1201 height=726 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/552edb435397aad6e4b848023484ea2f.avif?t=1770897818\" width=476 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在单机模式下体验沉浸式剧情，也可以在联机模式中，和朋友一起种田、经营、冒险，享受一段欢闹时光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/03ff80e8616740a3069c9d368729205d.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/03ff80e8616740a3069c9d368729205d.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/03ff80e8616740a3069c9d368729205d.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/95343dcb75c744a3a7b7639e860ef9d3.avif?t=1770897818\" width=493 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择扮演兄妹中的任意一人或是创造一个属于你自己的角色，开始独属于你的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发型、肤色、表情···多种装扮选项帮助你打扮出最喜欢的形象，在启程前，不妨先好好打扮一番做好准备吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/9309f98c63e75070b172ec8814efeabf.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/9309f98c63e75070b172ec8814efeabf.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/9309f98c63e75070b172ec8814efeabf.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/6b0f3408e8db6fe316e0f747b5bc9496.avif?t=1770897818\" width=493 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在风景优美的海滨农场，你可以通过种植庄稼、钓鱼和搜集资源，也可以从码头出发，乘船前往其他地图，探索未知世界，在探索中收集稀有藏品，揭开世界背后的神秘传奇，了解不一样的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/fd61481b9411f25e797a53b6065173af.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/fd61481b9411f25e797a53b6065173af.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/fd61481b9411f25e797a53b6065173af.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/0000f3fae92f2f536bd671a0d697462c.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/0000f3fae92f2f536bd671a0d697462c.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/0000f3fae92f2f536bd671a0d697462c.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/8261eff474e585166b08f2ebc79169f5.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/8261eff474e585166b08f2ebc79169f5.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/8261eff474e585166b08f2ebc79169f5.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/20cb69bc0756c26b72f03e99a94d062c.avif?t=1770897818\" width=493 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可可爱爱，充满活力！拥有神奇能力的宠物来帮你！无论是增加产量还是减少种植时间，统统没问题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/3ae05bafec93a50b8680fd26bd3f2622.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/3ae05bafec93a50b8680fd26bd3f2622.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/3ae05bafec93a50b8680fd26bd3f2622.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/5ffe7497855572225fa5f6bbfabe69bb.avif?t=1770897818\" width=493 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索中收集到足够的食材和材料后，不如回到小岛，用这些精心准备的菜品经营你的小酒馆，招待每一位被美酒与美食吸引而来的顾客！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/ad0ca699fb4368b9621d48fab661d358.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/ad0ca699fb4368b9621d48fab661d358.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/ad0ca699fb4368b9621d48fab661d358.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/a896868cd05e9bc70c6d7ca5eac4c0a3.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/a896868cd05e9bc70c6d7ca5eac4c0a3.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/a896868cd05e9bc70c6d7ca5eac4c0a3.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/0cbfd0206a76d9e4d14405bb2aa9c67b.poster.avif?t=1770897818\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/0cbfd0206a76d9e4d14405bb2aa9c67b.webm?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148160/extras/0cbfd0206a76d9e4d14405bb2aa9c67b.mp4?t=1770897818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >愿你能享受这个世界带给你的种种乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来加入你的愿望单，开启一段既惬意又充满惊喜的美食与冒险之旅吧！每一份支持都是我们前进的动力。你的心愿单不仅是对我们的鼓励，更是助力我们不断打造更更好游戏体验的动力！加入愿望单，与我们一起见证这个奇幻世界的成长与发展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
